These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
Sport: soccer, cycling
Food: cabbage, cauliflower
1. Sport:soccer is on the left of Food:cabbage##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Sport   | soccer  | cycling |
| Food     | cauliflower | cabbage  |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
Color: turquise, coral
Game: go, backgammon
1. Color:coral is on the right of Game:go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Color    | turquise      | coral         |
| Game   | go | backgammon |

